{"title":"[CodeRead] TiKV Importer","date":"2021-03-17T11:51:36.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 17, 2021","L":"03/17/2021","MM-DD":"03-17"},"link":"2021/03/17/tikv-importer","tags":["TiDB"],"categories":["DB"],"updated":"2021-03-21T15:45:51.451Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tikv/importer\" target=\"_blank\">Importer</a> 是一个为 TiKV 设计的数据导入工具，使用 Rust 编写。支持 batch 和 streaming 两种导入模式。</p>\n<p>从 TiKV 4.0 开始，Importer 已经处于半 deprecated 的状态了，文档也比较缺乏。所以，本文从代码的角度，尝试分析一下 Importer 的原理。</p>\n<h2 id=\"server\">Server<a title=\"#server\" href=\"#server\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"service\">Service<a title=\"#service\" href=\"#service\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"importer\">Importer<a title=\"#importer\" href=\"#importer\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"engine\">Engine<a title=\"#engine\" href=\"#engine\"></a></h2>\n","prev":{"title":"[CodeRead] TiDB Lightning","link":"2021/03/19/tidb-lightning"},"next":{"title":"[Tutorial] Kubernetes Ramp Up","link":"2021/03/15/k8s-ramp-up"},"plink":"https://blog.abingcbc.cn/2021/03/17/tikv-importer/","toc":[{"id":"server","title":"Server","index":"1"},{"id":"service","title":"Service","index":"2"},{"id":"importer","title":"Importer","index":"3"},{"id":"engine","title":"Engine","index":"4"}],"copyright":{"author":"Bingchang Chen","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.abingcbc.cn/2021/03/17/tikv-importer/\" title=\"[CodeRead] TiKV Importer\">https://blog.abingcbc.cn/2021/03/17/tikv-importer/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}